<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4"><strong>Reasoning & Chat Models:</strong></p>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-4">
<li>Claude (full series including Claude 3.5 Sonnet, Opus)</li>
<li>GPT-4o / GPT-4o-mini / GPT-4 Turbo</li>
<li>Gemini 2.5 Pro / Gemini 2.5 Flash</li>
