<li>firefunction-2 / firefunction-1 (Fireworks AI)</li>
<li>Claude Code (full modes)</li>
<li>OpenAI Codex (full modes)</li>
</ul>
<p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">The platform claims "more models added continuously." The model count of 50+ makes BAI competitive with OpenRouter in breadth, though OpenRouter offers more granular provider-level routing.</p>
